Thanks for taking a look at Bubblegum!

Bubblegum is a simple tool for sharing files with your friends. Our aims is to make software that will let groups of people securely and easily share data.

Philosphy:
* Bubblegum is free software. (Beer + Speech)
* Bubblegum is simple. No complicated settings, no ridiculous preferences.
* Bubblegum is safe. Share only with who you want.

Resources:
* Code repository: http://github.com/waltz/bubblegum/tree/master
* Documentation wiki: http://github.com/waltz/bubblegum/wiki